{"tid":741771,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［醫療撚］解決醫療事故方法？","createTime":"2018-07-14T03:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T08:29:28.000Z","uid":19725,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d1ba1d522ab945337cd8259c852a6977a3275910","tid":741771,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T03:38:57.000Z","msg":"其實咁多醫療事故都係源於人太多 症太多<br />\n公立醫院不如淨係provide primary &amp; secondary care 同埋有權將高死亡率既症轉介返大陸 咁咪大家都開心？<br />\n<br />\n香港人都係想咁姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我同你講 醫療事故係全世界甚至美國都有 人地美國放落醫療GDP 成幾十% 香港得個4-5% 我真係笑而不語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 極有機會政府用民粹引入海外（內地）醫生（自己睇邊個國家既人考得最多執業試） <br />\n<br />\n個班醫生連廣東話都唔識講 要全部人就佢 電腦又唔識人 大家入醫院自求多福 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df751dda88e0ea50548a60370960779e99551d6","tid":741771,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T08:29:28.000Z","msg":"單程證黎香港嗰d趕返去中國咪解決左問題"}]}